  <li id="comment-15813" class="comment even thread-even depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="https://www.blogger.com/profile/01493708300940204826" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">Molly</a></cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2009/02/now-you-know/#comment-15813"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2009-03-14T03:16:00-04:00">Saturday, March 14, 2009 at 3:16 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Lucia, I do think you could freeze this soup, yes, but I would leave out the sour cream mixture.  I worry that it would do something strange in the freezing and thawing process.  Instead, maybe add it after the soup is thawed, when you rewarm it?</p>
    </div>

